      <description>&lt;p&gt;Jörg Dörr holds the &amp;ldquo;Digital Farming&amp;rdquo; chair at the TU Kaiserslautern. He has also been a member of the extended institute management of Fraunhofer IESE in Kaiserslautern since 2020. He is responsible for the institute&amp;rsquo;s research programs and has been in charge of the &amp;ldquo;Smart Farming&amp;rdquo; program at the institute since 2020.&lt;/p&gt;
